title: Hummus Republic
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Assembly-line Mediterranean cuisine bar, inside the mall. Also an outlet at Westfield Topanga mall. Offers 3 daily hummus, salads with your choice of dressing, create-your-own pita. Has a seitan EarthBurger, a falafel burger. Specify if you are vegan when ordering.
